{"item_id":"reader_A_01","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"A","material_no":1,"question_code":"Q13","concept_key":"projectile_motion","concept_label_zh":"抛体运动","concept_id":"C04","domain":"Physics","visible_text":"阅读材料1：篮球离手以后。\n有人问：“篮球被投出去以后，水平方向还受不受力？”\n这段材料给出的答案是：不受向前的力。篮球离手以后，手已经不再推它；它之所以继续向前，是因为惯性让它保持原来的水平运动状态。","visible_text_sha256":"129767c542cc331f8964f791ac9786011e914888935ed61fe378d724123902fb","visible_text_char_count":101,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":297,"comprehension_question":"若忽略空气阻力，一个小球被水平抛出后，为什么它还能继续向前运动？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_A_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"7fa06d7710adda9ded2d616b0df789f81718b2f82e9b6d0c82d1266b54a34588","source_container_sha256":"a896a0b68f198ed9fac3bd93589201d225e6346698f203c280789cdc878e4084","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_A|A|1","mapped_item_id":"千问_C_C04","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_064","generator":"Alibaba Qwen","upstream_task":"C","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_A_02","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"A","material_no":2,"question_code":"Q14","concept_key":"evolution_no_goal","concept_label_zh":"进化没有预设目标","concept_id":"C14","domain":"Biology","visible_text":"阅读材料2：完美的陷阱。\n小其以为，进化会一步步造出越来越完美的生物。老师摇摇头说：“不一定。生物只要能适应当前环境，就可能保留下来。进化没有提前设定好的目标，也不一定追求完美。”","visible_text_sha256":"a91dc810f66283998586f55616d913a8f5c33184e1043a8452f0e63b518c5587","visible_text_char_count":90,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":266,"comprehension_question":"如果某种动物在环境中保留下来，最合理的解释是？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_A_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"7fa06d7710adda9ded2d616b0df789f81718b2f82e9b6d0c82d1266b54a34588","source_container_sha256":"a896a0b68f198ed9fac3bd93589201d225e6346698f203c280789cdc878e4084","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_A|A|2","mapped_item_id":"DEEPSEEK_B_C14","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_314","generator":"DeepSeek","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_A_03","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"A","material_no":3,"question_code":"Q15","concept_key":"geological_time","concept_label_zh":"地质时间","concept_id":"C20","domain":"Geoscience","visible_text":"阅读材料3：像指甲一样慢的板块。\n老师说，地球板块的移动很慢，有点像指甲生长。几年、几十年里，人们很难直接看出变化。\n这段材料想说明：很多地质变化发生在很长的时间尺度上，远远超过一个人的日常经验。","visible_text_sha256":"bbbb5f43784f809c198b104ab9205311fb588b4df34fbc7cc1dbc87c9c90af1a","visible_text_char_count":98,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":288,"comprehension_question":"关于“板块移动像指甲生长”这个类比，以下理解更准确的是？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_A_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"7fa06d7710adda9ded2d616b0df789f81718b2f82e9b6d0c82d1266b54a34588","source_container_sha256":"a896a0b68f198ed9fac3bd93589201d225e6346698f203c280789cdc878e4084","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_A|A|3","mapped_item_id":"DEEPSEEK_B_C20","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_320","generator":"DeepSeek","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_A_04","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"A","material_no":4,"question_code":"Q16","concept_key":"plant_respiration","concept_label_zh":"光合作用与细胞呼吸","concept_id":"C18","domain":"Biology","visible_text":"阅读材料4：夜间的盆栽。\n夜晚的卧室里没有阳光，绿萝仍然在进行生命活动。它会吸收氧气、释放二氧化碳，并通过这个过程获得维持生命所需的能量。\n这段材料想说明：植物也会进行呼吸作用。","visible_text_sha256":"df546a2e19151618ad7a16d147bfbfe0137eaba193fa99efc5b0835f087e15fc","visible_text_char_count":89,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":261,"comprehension_question":"黑暗中绿萝吸收氧气、释放二氧化碳，最能说明什么？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_A_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"7fa06d7710adda9ded2d616b0df789f81718b2f82e9b6d0c82d1266b54a34588","source_container_sha256":"a896a0b68f198ed9fac3bd93589201d225e6346698f203c280789cdc878e4084","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_A|A|4","mapped_item_id":"Gemini_B_C18","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_408","generator":"Google Gemini","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_A_05","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"A","material_no":5,"question_code":"Q17","concept_key":"adaptation","concept_label_zh":"进化没有预设目标","concept_id":"C14","domain":"Biology","visible_text":"阅读材料5：进化不一定越来越复杂。\n有些人以为，进化就是生物从“低级”一步步变成“高级”。\n这段材料认为：生物进化没有固定方向。环境会影响哪些变异更容易保留下来，适应当前环境就可能成功，进化不一定总是变复杂。","visible_text_sha256":"185f4218daf7d457e8505e8d7c8c58de0a93df6d333be7c1428c8d5f452aae1d","visible_text_char_count":104,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":306,"comprehension_question":"关于“进化不总是变复杂”，以下哪项最准确？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_A_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"7fa06d7710adda9ded2d616b0df789f81718b2f82e9b6d0c82d1266b54a34588","source_container_sha256":"a896a0b68f198ed9fac3bd93589201d225e6346698f203c280789cdc878e4084","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_A|A|5","mapped_item_id":"GLM_A_C14","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_734","generator":"Zhipu GLM","upstream_task":"A","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_A_06","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"A","material_no":6,"question_code":"Q18","concept_key":"net_force_vs_velocity","concept_label_zh":"净力与加速度","concept_id":"C02","domain":"Physics","visible_text":"阅读材料6：推车为什么会越来越快。\n小艾推购物车时，车越推越快。朋友问：“是不是力越大，速度就越大？”\n这段材料给出的提醒是：净力决定的是加速度，也就是速度变化的快慢；它不是直接决定速度本身。","visible_text_sha256":"5926132b8302652daa79bd1458c7b679394b1eefda86a2b9867f245f2448a860","visible_text_char_count":96,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":282,"comprehension_question":"一辆车在平直路面上保持很大的恒定速度运动时，以下哪项更准确？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_A_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"7fa06d7710adda9ded2d616b0df789f81718b2f82e9b6d0c82d1266b54a34588","source_container_sha256":"a896a0b68f198ed9fac3bd93589201d225e6346698f203c280789cdc878e4084","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_A|A|6","mapped_item_id":"DEEPSEEK_B_C02","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_302","generator":"DeepSeek","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_B_01","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"B","material_no":1,"question_code":"Q13","concept_key":"projectile_motion","concept_label_zh":"抛体运动","concept_id":"C04","domain":"Physics","visible_text":"阅读材料1：篮球为什么还能向前飞。\n篮球被投出去以后，手已经离开篮球，不会继续给它向前的推力。如果先用一个简化模型，暂时忽略空气阻力，那么篮球在水平方向上没有持续的外力。它还能继续向前飞，是因为它会保持离手前已有的水平运动状态。与此同时，重力会让它向下落。在真实环境中，空气阻力也会逐渐影响篮球的运动。","visible_text_sha256":"00007c0f6079d4def1f0f554da96ad375327ad6dbebde59310c36bb361266d0a","visible_text_char_count":151,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":449,"comprehension_question":"若忽略空气阻力，一个小球被水平抛出后，为什么它还能继续向前运动？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_B_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cfc507f351f651223b7810f0da553ac388672f419ac4ebafeb7198636cd73e28","source_container_sha256":"2c6247ffbbe260e1015fca293e12d41d9fbe3c34b65402f6d27d84ba1a5793e7","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_B|B|1","mapped_item_id":"千问_C_C04","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_064","generator":"Alibaba Qwen","upstream_task":"C","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_B_02","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"B","material_no":2,"question_code":"Q14","concept_key":"evolution_no_goal","concept_label_zh":"进化没有预设目标","concept_id":"C14","domain":"Biology","visible_text":"阅读材料2：进化不是奔向完美。\n进化并不是按照某个计划去制造“完美生物”。在一个生物群体里，个体之间会有可遗传的差异。某些差异如果刚好更适合当前环境，就可能让这些个体更容易生存和繁殖。这样一代代积累下来，群体就会发生变化。所以，“适应”只是在某个环境中更合适，不等于完美，也不等于更高级。","visible_text_sha256":"06a41a6756015352844d09343bec7398a7a4e630bfc5afae549dc9af984af3dc","visible_text_char_count":144,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":428,"comprehension_question":"如果某种动物在环境中保留下来，最合理的解释是？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_B_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cfc507f351f651223b7810f0da553ac388672f419ac4ebafeb7198636cd73e28","source_container_sha256":"2c6247ffbbe260e1015fca293e12d41d9fbe3c34b65402f6d27d84ba1a5793e7","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_B|B|2","mapped_item_id":"DEEPSEEK_B_C14","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_314","generator":"DeepSeek","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_B_03","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"B","material_no":3,"question_code":"Q15","concept_key":"geological_time","concept_label_zh":"地质时间","concept_id":"C20","domain":"Geoscience","visible_text":"阅读材料3：慢变化也能造成大结果。\n很多地质过程在人类日常生活中看起来非常慢。比如，板块一年可能只移动几厘米，短时间内几乎看不出变化。但地球的时间尺度很长。几百万年甚至更久以后，这些很小的移动会不断累积，可能形成山脉、改变海陆位置，带来巨大的地质结果。同时，也有一些地质事件会在短时间内突然发生。","visible_text_sha256":"45570a054b7e21616343a19ec1ebaa0f577b3a2d6ba68288e6dffe967ae5b305","visible_text_char_count":148,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":440,"comprehension_question":"关于“板块移动像指甲生长”这个类比，以下理解更准确的是？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_B_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cfc507f351f651223b7810f0da553ac388672f419ac4ebafeb7198636cd73e28","source_container_sha256":"2c6247ffbbe260e1015fca293e12d41d9fbe3c34b65402f6d27d84ba1a5793e7","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_B|B|3","mapped_item_id":"DEEPSEEK_B_C20","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_320","generator":"DeepSeek","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_B_04","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"B","material_no":4,"question_code":"Q16","concept_key":"plant_respiration","concept_label_zh":"光合作用与细胞呼吸","concept_id":"C18","domain":"Biology","visible_text":"阅读材料4：植物白天和夜晚都在呼吸。\n植物既会进行光合作用，也会进行细胞呼吸。光合作用需要光。它把二氧化碳和水变成有机物，并释放氧气。细胞呼吸则是把有机物分解，释放生命活动需要的能量，通常会消耗氧气并释放二氧化碳。植物白天需要能量，夜晚也需要能量，所以白天和夜晚都会进行细胞呼吸。","visible_text_sha256":"7d107c521a368d49dee979673b8a5f527c057f5d989a9d99eaa5e569579532c7","visible_text_char_count":140,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":416,"comprehension_question":"黑暗中绿萝吸收氧气、释放二氧化碳，最能说明什么？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_B_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cfc507f351f651223b7810f0da553ac388672f419ac4ebafeb7198636cd73e28","source_container_sha256":"2c6247ffbbe260e1015fca293e12d41d9fbe3c34b65402f6d27d84ba1a5793e7","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_B|B|4","mapped_item_id":"Gemini_B_C18","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_408","generator":"Google Gemini","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_B_05","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"B","material_no":5,"question_code":"Q17","concept_key":"adaptation","concept_label_zh":"进化没有预设目标","concept_id":"C14","domain":"Biology","visible_text":"阅读材料5：简单也可能是一种适应。\n进化中的变异不是生物“想要什么”就会产生什么。变异先出现，环境再影响哪些变异更容易被保留下来。这也意味着，进化不一定朝着复杂、高级或类似人类的方向前进。有些环境中，简单的结构反而更省能量、更适合生存。因此，变简单也可能是一种适应。","visible_text_sha256":"13c2377f8265a12ebc6d75efde2cab38e9c9ef8018a54ef26e95f7561750769b","visible_text_char_count":133,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":395,"comprehension_question":"关于“进化不总是变复杂”，以下哪项最准确？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_B_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cfc507f351f651223b7810f0da553ac388672f419ac4ebafeb7198636cd73e28","source_container_sha256":"2c6247ffbbe260e1015fca293e12d41d9fbe3c34b65402f6d27d84ba1a5793e7","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_B|B|5","mapped_item_id":"GLM_A_C14","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_734","generator":"Zhipu GLM","upstream_task":"A","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_B_06","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"B","material_no":6,"question_code":"Q18","concept_key":"net_force_vs_velocity","concept_label_zh":"净力与加速度","concept_id":"C02","domain":"Physics","visible_text":"阅读材料6：速度大不等于净力大。\n在力学里，净力决定的是加速度，也就是速度怎样改变。如果一个物体的速度越来越大，说明它有加速度，通常也说明有净力在改变它的运动。但如果一个物体只是以很大的速度匀速直线运动，它的速度并没有变化，加速度就是零。这时，它受到的净力也可以是零或近似为零。","visible_text_sha256":"93ef670f33a046f8c9653354a6eae80fe54cf8807d8d8c4aae2107c63fdc0d13","visible_text_char_count":139,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":413,"comprehension_question":"一辆车在平直路面上保持很大的恒定速度运动时，以下哪项更准确？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_B_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cfc507f351f651223b7810f0da553ac388672f419ac4ebafeb7198636cd73e28","source_container_sha256":"2c6247ffbbe260e1015fca293e12d41d9fbe3c34b65402f6d27d84ba1a5793e7","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_B|B|6","mapped_item_id":"DEEPSEEK_B_C02","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_302","generator":"DeepSeek","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_C_01","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"C","material_no":1,"question_code":"Q13","concept_key":"projectile_motion","concept_label_zh":"抛体运动","concept_id":"C04","domain":"Physics","visible_text":"阅读材料1：篮球离手后，力还在吗？\n很多人看到篮球还在向前飞，就会觉得“它一定还受到一个向前的力”。这个想法很自然，但它把“正在运动”和“正在受力”混在了一起。在忽略空气阻力的理想模型中，篮球离手以后，手不再推它，水平方向也没有持续的合力。它继续向前，是因为物体会保持原来的水平速度。真实比赛里还会有空气阻力、旋转和碰撞等因素，但这些是进一步分析时才加入的条件。","visible_text_sha256":"0750c04a60221d3678629f17bdb60316cbdda5643706a794f50ca55a81d8e0b5","visible_text_char_count":181,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":539,"comprehension_question":"若忽略空气阻力，一个小球被水平抛出后，为什么它还能继续向前运动？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_C_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cf175ec0b7806356fb7014d0c422e1764c950622f9968aadc3a5de2acbc232f3","source_container_sha256":"6e47579f8d33664408e75b932511fe366cd259570c4e4a0896f27829112188dc","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_C|C|1","mapped_item_id":"千问_C_C04","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_064","generator":"Alibaba Qwen","upstream_task":"C","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_C_02","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"C","material_no":2,"question_code":"Q14","concept_key":"evolution_no_goal","concept_label_zh":"进化没有预设目标","concept_id":"C14","domain":"Biology","visible_text":"阅读材料2：进化没有提前写好的终点。\n“进化会造出完美生物”是一种常见误解。自然选择没有提前设定好的终点，也不会预先知道未来需要什么。更准确地说，一个群体中本来就会有可遗传的差异。某些差异如果更适合当前环境，就会让个体更容易留下后代。可是环境会变，今天有利的特征，明天未必仍然有利。所以，适应不是完美，也不是朝“更高级”方向攀升。","visible_text_sha256":"479be42075e3821668e0731653e5211b34c78db32b5486711ec20df04afef4e4","visible_text_char_count":165,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":491,"comprehension_question":"如果某种动物在环境中保留下来，最合理的解释是？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_C_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cf175ec0b7806356fb7014d0c422e1764c950622f9968aadc3a5de2acbc232f3","source_container_sha256":"6e47579f8d33664408e75b932511fe366cd259570c4e4a0896f27829112188dc","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_C|C|2","mapped_item_id":"DEEPSEEK_B_C14","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_314","generator":"DeepSeek","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_C_03","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"C","material_no":3,"question_code":"Q15","concept_key":"geological_time","concept_label_zh":"地质时间","concept_id":"C20","domain":"Geoscience","visible_text":"阅读材料3：为什么地质时间让人难以想象。\n地质时间难理解，是因为它远远超过人的日常经验。板块一年移动几厘米，看起来几乎没有变化；可是如果把时间拉长到几百万年，这些小变化就可能改变海陆位置、形成山脉，甚至打开新的海盆。不过，“很多地质过程很慢”并不等于“所有地质现象都慢”。地震、火山喷发、滑坡等事件可能在短时间内发生，它们常常是长期积累后的快速释放。","visible_text_sha256":"6c7eaacd12e1b214645fb23be433998d4a6fcf387cc61ebbd85ca43c1b835bbc","visible_text_char_count":175,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":521,"comprehension_question":"关于“板块移动像指甲生长”这个类比，以下理解更准确的是？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_C_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cf175ec0b7806356fb7014d0c422e1764c950622f9968aadc3a5de2acbc232f3","source_container_sha256":"6e47579f8d33664408e75b932511fe366cd259570c4e4a0896f27829112188dc","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_C|C|3","mapped_item_id":"DEEPSEEK_B_C20","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_320","generator":"DeepSeek","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_C_04","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"C","material_no":4,"question_code":"Q16","concept_key":"plant_respiration","concept_label_zh":"光合作用与细胞呼吸","concept_id":"C18","domain":"Biology","visible_text":"阅读材料4：植物不是晚上才“呼吸”。\n很多人会把植物理解成“白天光合作用，晚上才呼吸”。这个说法太简单了。细胞呼吸是细胞获得能量的基本过程，植物白天和夜晚都要进行。光合作用需要光，主要是在有光时把二氧化碳转化为有机物，并释放氧气。细胞呼吸则分解有机物来释放能量，通常会消耗氧气并释放二氧化碳。夜间更容易观察到植物释放二氧化碳，是因为没有光合作用来抵消这一表现。","visible_text_sha256":"debd484e21cbc69e4e5252a8fd6ae9c9813c48c2bb10c0db71e6b7d089244b86","visible_text_char_count":180,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":536,"comprehension_question":"黑暗中绿萝吸收氧气、释放二氧化碳，最能说明什么？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_C_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cf175ec0b7806356fb7014d0c422e1764c950622f9968aadc3a5de2acbc232f3","source_container_sha256":"6e47579f8d33664408e75b932511fe366cd259570c4e4a0896f27829112188dc","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_C|C|4","mapped_item_id":"Gemini_B_C18","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_408","generator":"Google Gemini","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_C_05","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"C","material_no":5,"question_code":"Q17","concept_key":"adaptation","concept_label_zh":"进化没有预设目标","concept_id":"C14","domain":"Biology","visible_text":"阅读材料5：进化不是从低级走向高级。\n“生物总会从低级进化到高级”听起来很顺，但并不是进化的通用路线。进化首先依赖群体中的可遗传变异，而这些变异不是按生物的需要定制出来的。环境会影响哪些变异更容易传给后代，但选择只针对当前环境中的生存和繁殖结果。在寄生生活、洞穴生活或稳定环境中，结构变简单也可能更合适。因此，复杂不等于更进化，简单也不等于落后。","visible_text_sha256":"931de414d2e0b2b70b49ebd634c052be8ab2715a134bb24f64ac30ce8314f5e7","visible_text_char_count":173,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":515,"comprehension_question":"关于“进化不总是变复杂”，以下哪项最准确？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_C_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cf175ec0b7806356fb7014d0c422e1764c950622f9968aadc3a5de2acbc232f3","source_container_sha256":"6e47579f8d33664408e75b932511fe366cd259570c4e4a0896f27829112188dc","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_C|C|5","mapped_item_id":"GLM_A_C14","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_734","generator":"Zhipu GLM","upstream_task":"A","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
{"item_id":"reader_C_06","experiment_id":"api_reader_bridge_18","version":"C","material_no":6,"question_code":"Q18","concept_key":"net_force_vs_velocity","concept_label_zh":"净力与加速度","concept_id":"C02","domain":"Physics","visible_text":"阅读材料6：力不是直接决定速度大小。\n“力越大，速度就越大”是学习力学时很常见的误解。更准确地说，净力决定的是加速度，也就是速度怎样改变。比如，推购物车时车越推越快，是因为存在向前的净力，让车的速度增加。可是当车已经以稳定速度前进时，推动力可能主要是在抵消阻力，而不是继续让速度变大。如果一个物体速度很大但保持不变，它的加速度就是零，净力也可以是零或近似为零。","visible_text_sha256":"32041e3f1e26e235648940f68b4bf9504ef6d9e2cd4da4eb5fb9768a02ee2a8e","visible_text_char_count":180,"visible_text_utf8_bytes":536,"comprehension_question":"一辆车在平直路面上保持很大的恒定速度运动时，以下哪项更准确？","source_provenance":{"instrument_file":"public_form_C_instrument.txt","instrument_sha256":"cf175ec0b7806356fb7014d0c422e1764c950622f9968aadc3a5de2acbc232f3","source_container_sha256":"6e47579f8d33664408e75b932511fe366cd259570c4e4a0896f27829112188dc","crosswalk_row_key":"public_reader_ABC|public_reader_C|C|6","mapped_item_id":"DEEPSEEK_B_C02","legacy_item_id":"ITEM_302","generator":"DeepSeek","upstream_task":"B","map_status":"provenance_confirmed_one_to_one","mapping_confidence":"high"}}
